                                    </div>
                                    <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapseNinetysix" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingNinetysix">
                                        <div class="panel-body pxlr-faq-body">
                                            <p>For now XinFin doesn't support hardware wallet but it will support soon.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-default">
                                    <div class="panel-heading" id="headingNinetyseven" role="tab">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion5" href="#collapseNinetyseven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNinetyseven">19) Can I store XDCE on XinFin Wallet ?</a></h4>
