                                    <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapseHundredfour" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingHundredfour">
                                        <div class="panel-body pxlr-faq-body">
                                            <p>Yes <strong>XinFin network is Ethereum compatible</strong>, so you can deploy any smart contract on xinfin.network.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-default">
                                    <div class="panel-heading" id="headingHundredfive" role="tab">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion5" href="#collapseHundredfive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseHundredfive">27) Can we create a ERC-20 token on XinFin network ?</a></h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapseHundredfive" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingHundredfive">
                                        <div class="panel-body pxlr-faq-body">
                                            <p>Yes you can create your own token on XinFin network with Mycontract.
                                                <br>Read : <a href="https://medium.com/xinfin/a-step-by-step-guide-to-issue-your-own-token-on-xinfin-network-in-a-few-minutes-b03aeae3be69">How to Deploy own token on XinFin Network</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
