                                    <div class="panel-heading" id="headingHundredsix" role="tab">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseHundredsix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseHundredsix">01) What is the recommended way to access your wallet ?</a>
